    ExecuteWorkerFlatMap<R extends TrainingResult>
    A FlatMapFunction for executing training on DataSets.

    A FlatMapFunction for executing training on MultiDataSets.
    ExecuteWorkerPathFlatMap<R extends TrainingResult>
    A FlatMapFunction for executing training on serialized DataSet objects, that can be loaded from a path (local or HDFS) that is specified as a String Used in both SparkDl4jMultiLayer and SparkComputationGraph implementations
